extends layout

block content
  //- Source: https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/node-js/tags-in-pug-view-engine/
  .about_us_page
    .header_container
      img.dark_logo(src="/images/Downtown_Donuts_Dark_Background.png" alt="Logo")
      h1.company_title= title
    h2 About Us

    .about_us_paragraphs
      // About us text generated with Copilot
      p Welcome to Downtown Donuts, where every donut is made with love and a sprinkle of hometown pride. 
        | We’re a small, family‑owned shop that’s been part of the downtown community since 1992 — a place 
        | where mornings start with laughter, the smell of fresh coffee fills the air, and friends gather 
        | around a box of warm donuts. What began as a simple dream has grown into a cozy corner where 
        | neighbors feel like family and every visit feels like coming home.

      p Our kitchen is our heart. Each batch is hand‑crafted daily using simple, quality ingredients and 
        | family recipes passed down through generations. We still roll, glaze, and decorate our donuts 
        | the same way we did on day one — with care, patience, and a whole lot of joy. Whether you’re 
        | here for a classic glazed, a seasonal favorite, or just a friendly chat at the counter, we want 
        | you to feel right at home. There’s always a warm donut ready and a warm smile waiting.

      p At Downtown Donuts, we believe in more than sweet treats — we believe in connection. Over the 
        | years, we’ve watched first dates turn into anniversaries, kids grow up and bring their own 
        | families, and countless morning traditions form around our little shop. Stop by, share a smile, 
        | and taste the comfort of something made by hand, right here in the neighborhood. We’re grateful 
        | to be part of your day, your memories, and your community — one donut at a time.
      // End of generated text

    //- Creates the buttons to navigate to the other pages 
    footer
      button(type='button', class='goToMenu') Go to the Menu Page
      button(type='button', class='goToLandingPage') Go to the Landing Page
      button(type='button', class='goToCustomerComments') Go to the Customer Comments Page